=head1 DESCRIPTION

Determines whether CloudFront includes the C<Referrer-Policy> HTTP
response header and the header's value.

For more information about the C<Referrer-Policy> HTTP response header,
see Referrer-Policy
(https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Referrer-Policy)
in the MDN Web Docs.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Override => Bool

A Boolean that determines whether CloudFront overrides the
C<Referrer-Policy> HTTP response header received from the origin with
the one specified in this response headers policy.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> ReferrerPolicy => Str

The value of the C<Referrer-Policy> HTTP response header. Valid values
are:

=over

=item *

C<no-referrer>

=item *

C<no-referrer-when-downgrade>

=item *

C<origin>

=item *

C<origin-when-cross-origin>

=item *

C<same-origin>

=item *

C<strict-origin>

=item *

C<strict-origin-when-cross-origin>

=item *

C<unsafe-url>

=back

For more information about these values, see Referrer-Policy
(https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Referrer-Policy)
in the MDN Web Docs.



